Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:03.19,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Central Nations have made their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:07.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We believe they're planning a Third Crusade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to revive the church's dwindling influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:14.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The White Night King, the one man the Centrals could influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was essentially dethroned after his disastrous loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:20.29,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,Then the heroic Winter King appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and captivated the people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:28.46,Default,Ym,0000,0000,0000,,just in time for them to feel the effects of the food surplus they really owed to the Crimson Scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,With their guard dog off its chain, the church must be panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.57,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to do anything as the Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:41.10,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,we must first form a new Council of Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.55,Default,Old Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.60,Default,Old Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,A diplomat from the Ice Country is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:50.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}{First white frame}
