Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.85,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to be annoying for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.85,0:01:08.81,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I don't mind being conceited
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.81,0:01:12.85,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hide a tree in a forest, they say
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.36,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}It started with a little mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.36,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's redo our meeting from there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.36,0:01:24.82,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's oppose the strand of time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.58,0:01:30.79,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Strength alone is no weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.87,0:01:38.96,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}You taught me that just now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.96,0:01:44.47,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to show you what lies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.47,0:01:50.68,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}beyond these days
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.68,0:01:53.23,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}The wind is strong
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.23,0:01:56.31,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I'm sure you know that too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.31,0:02:01.15,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.15,0:02:07.95,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Sharing makes you dependant
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.95,0:02:11.12,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now, take my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.67,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hold it tight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.96,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now...
