Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.83,Titles,Old Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H64DAFC&\blur0.6\shad2\4c&H000E13&\pos(935.143,347.714)}I Am Human
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:28.01,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.25,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.05,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,You hail from the Bard Country,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where dance and flowery words rule all, which is exactly what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.73,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What would you have me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:40.82,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop whatever the current Council of Ten is doing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gather some information for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.48,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,If you need help, just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.59,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.03,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.66,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,you're attempting to buy time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.83,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I require not victory, but time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:01.34,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Does the same not go for your teacher, the Crimson Scholar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.21,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only skills are dancing and spreading rumors, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.79,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the place we're headed is a battlefield all its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.82,Default,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can definitely say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that nothing will get the better of me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.97,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.14,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The Crimson Scholar can't be a heretic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty crazy down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them are saying she's a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.88,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The peasants all love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.21,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.35,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever my sister and I walk down the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone smiles and waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.76,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at all the potatoes we harvested this spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.72,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"This fall, we're raising plenty of wheat."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.22,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,They offer us berries
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.10,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,or give us eggs to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.86,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Or even quails.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.15,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,There was never a day when our table was without some gift from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:26.66,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,They were all wonderful people, and they loved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.16,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"Take good care of the Scholar," they would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.39,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"She's done so much for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.67,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't do anything for her."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.50,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.51,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, they'd bring a baby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have me touch its tiny little hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.96,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"So that she may grow to be smart and kind like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.14,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I was a mere serf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.19,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,But they called me important because I served the Scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.89,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:00.11,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's doing what they can to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.53,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.53,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I should get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.95,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,As the leader of the Lakeside Convent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having to listen to some silver-tongued messenger's lecture annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.40,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.06,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.57,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.86,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on the surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.15,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.29,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.64,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.15,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.14,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.59,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.16,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.12,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,so powerless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.77,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.23,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.58,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.07,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,The peasants of the surrounding villages have come in force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.09,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I hope nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.24,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,The Messenger will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.56,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I'll post more guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.43,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.76,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.26,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.77,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,our King couldn't be so pale and seedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.96,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's the Messenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:45.48,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,He works for whoever is calling the Scholar a heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.40,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.80,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The King is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.49,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.54,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.83,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,You've brought her as promised, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.39,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.84,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,We'll turn her over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.69,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The Scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.68,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,It really is the Scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.68,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, this is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.98,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to fool us with a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.29,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That would be inconceivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.01,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this is her, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.00,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:54.32,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,The church thanks you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:58.69,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sure you must be pleased that we have found
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}no connection between you and the heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.14,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.43,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,People of the Winter Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.15,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.11,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,She is a servant of the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.61,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Align yourselves with her, and her fate awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.25,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take her to the Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.52,Default,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.34,Default,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Scholar, you couldn't be a heretic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.76,Default,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all that blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.06,Default,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,She'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:49.98,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they hitting my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.36,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,On your hands and knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.62,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Please control yourself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:06.33,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent girl, I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.71,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the world will have to atone for what it's done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.92,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the disobedience in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.16,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,They're the eyes of a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.73,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Does the servant of the demons who dares disobey
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Holy Light's teachings have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.31,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who has a soul not unlike you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.41,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born a serf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:53.47,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I was the third of seven siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.16,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,My brother broke his arm in the fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was left to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.57,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,One night, the land owner summoned my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.41,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,On a clear winter morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my youngest brother went cold and failed to wake from his slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.59,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Another sibling caught smallpox.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.35,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I was powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.51,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Only my sister and I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.22,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,And then, while we were on the run, we were given a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.48,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,It always seemed like fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.73,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,but something troubled me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.73,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,For so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:03.31,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Fate had been warm and kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.41,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't worry. I'll take care of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.99,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:10.99,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.86,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.15,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Pioneers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.76,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,And serfs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.76,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I must reject it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.05,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,even after all it's done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.64,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I must reject it because of all it's done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.77,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.06,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I still doubt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:42.78,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"The blood in your veins is that of a filthy serf."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:48.49,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,"You're just an insect, less than human."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.06,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,That is why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.62,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I must declare
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.54,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,that I am human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:02.89,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Because I believe the first step to being human is to say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.43,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever felt a warmth in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.45,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Like the summer sun on your cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.18,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,when you close your eyes, can't you still feel its blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:18.56,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever find happiness in simple acts of kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.21,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,That is the proof that you are human,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Holy Light's beloved children!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:24.57,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.12,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heretic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.83,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether I'm a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:37.17,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,As a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.37,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,As one to whom Winter's Passage Village has given so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.59,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I speak to my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:50.10,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you must never stop wishing, hoping, thinking, and working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:55.56,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,With her miracles, the Holy Light brought life to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:14:00.13,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,And with the earth's blessings, she brought us wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:05.23,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,And with her soul's fragments, she brought us freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.69,Default,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.72,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:12.13,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,The freedom to do better than you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.95,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,To be better than you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:19.79,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,The Light did not create us to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:23.71,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,She gave us the freedom to keep bettering ourselves, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.16,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Because that brings us joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:33.35,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,So don't relinquish that, just to make your lives easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.64,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,The Light's gifts are holy treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.64,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the King
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.35,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,or the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:44.14,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,can take them from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.86,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Heretic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.87,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,hold your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.87,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.16,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I am human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.88,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I will never surrender those treasures again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.35,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I won't return to being an insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.79,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much pain they bring,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.55,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I won't return to that haze of darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.17,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Because there is light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.79,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Because they were kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.81,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stone this heretic whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.02,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.52,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who refuses to stone her is an enemy of the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.89,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Throw them if you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.39,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you must,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect yourself and your family in this cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.33,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I will not blame you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:45.52,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,The freedom to choose also belongs to you, as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:51.84,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I will shed blood in equal measure to that which is flowing in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:59.85,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,But if you would stone me because someone else has ordered it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.85,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,then you are an insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.37,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,You are an insect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without a will of your own, for you have given the Light's precious gifts to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you have ceased to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.55,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much peace that brings you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone who abandons those treasures is no better than an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.41,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I despise insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.97,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.33,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.84,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I am human!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.70,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:50.19,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the rocks at the filthy whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.24,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.65,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,you disgusting, brainless serfs and peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all enemies of the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.45,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Winter King?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.21,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.30,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.45,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,her heresy is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:15.12,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Cut off her head at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.89,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.39,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:30.89,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You asked me to leave it in your hands, but I just couldn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.21,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Head Maid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never got the chance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But may I call you "teacher"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.41,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.35,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.59,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.22,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.56,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\i0}am the king of this nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.56,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I've been under the yoke of the Central Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:10.52,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I knew the pain, suffering, and disgust of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:16.01,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that, at heart, I had become an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.55,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,To be shown this by such a young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.53,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I am ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:28.04,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea such pride dwelt in the hearts of my people.{the truest victory, my son, is stirring the hearts of your people}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.00,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.42,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.63,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Messenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:40.64,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,As a servant of the Holy Light, your actions shame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.56,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,As do the actions of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.06,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,"You must master your sinful nature,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.90,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,said the Holy Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.48,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The freedom to sin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.77,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,is another gift we've been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:58.26,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:03.03,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I declare, here and now, that my country extends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its protection to the Crimson Scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:09.33,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,The Lakeside Convent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.58,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,hereby recognizes her as a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:17.05,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The King protected the Scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.43,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't a heretic, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.22,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,The nun said she's a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:27.68,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Our Scholar is a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.06,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.37,Default,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your own country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:34.94,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, Messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:39.87,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is all part of your plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we will meet again under different circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.45,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,For now, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:48.62,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you back for this, you nation of blasphemers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.96,Default,Me,0000,0000,0000,,After you've disobeyed the Holy Light's children,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you dare think this will all go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.65,Default,Blue Demon's Son,0000,0000,0000,,Why has my sealed eye gazed upon this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:25.45,Default,Blue Demon's Son,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who shall rule all the world eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.64,Default,Blue Demon's Son,0000,0000,0000,,What is it trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.19,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That was really amazing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:43.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Words alone can make an entire army withdraw.
