Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:08.15,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,1500)\xshad6\yshad-6\t(0,2000,\xshad4\yshad5)\4aAA\4c&H42333C&\blur0.6}The light is dim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:23.93,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,Before this hour, many lights have vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.19,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,On this little big planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:32.03,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,Each time a light disappears, pain shoots through my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.25,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,The blinking lights are birth and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.25,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,Just as he and I had hoped, the world may be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:42.92,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:45.21,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:46.84,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:51.09,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who tore the world asunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.96,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,This sin cannot be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.79,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,The warmth of fingers combing black hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:00.69,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,A long, long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:03.89,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,The words and caresses we shared,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:06.20,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,wind from the sky on our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:11.23,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet again, what should I say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.96,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want you to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.48,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,I can say but one thing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.32,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,"Salvation to all people,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:26.80,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,and eternal peace to all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.20,Default,Light Spirit,0000,0000,0000,,And if I could, I'd like to see you again."
